              <h2><a name="personal-safety" id="personal-safety"></a><br />
              <strong><a name="what-is-cp" id="what-is-cp"></a>What  is Club Penguin? </strong></h2>
              <table width="100" border="0" align="right" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0">
                <tr>
                  <td height="83" align="center" valign="middle"><p><a href="../help/tutorials/howto.htm" onmouseout="MM_swapImgRestore()" onmouseover="MM_swapImage('Image4','','../images/play-tutorial-blue-02.gif',1)"><img src="../images/play-tutorial-blue.gif" name="Image4" width="102" height="32" border="0" id="Image4" /></a><font face="Arial" color="navy" size="2"><span 
style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: navy; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"><br />
                  </span></font><span class="note" 
